review_blob: I just found this on tap locally, and being a sucker for new brands, I gave it a shot. I found this to be a very enjoyable stout! It has a strong roast bite on the front end with a slighty carmel sweet finish.  Didnt get the bitter aftertaste I find with most brands, which makes it one of the only stouts my wife will actually drink with me.  Ill add it to the shopping list!
